"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fjxHRoo30AwHqlUxdNisF.png?height=309&width=721)\\n\\n## About\\n\\nThe journey as a **Mundo Lingo Photographer** starts here.\\n\\nNot already in **The Dark Room?** First join [Mundo Lingo Collaborators](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/onyNgQAi-2VKGNTDGYK9vf20AK-k7i-3qot58G4Qo54) and then apply for residency here:\\n\\n[https://form.typeform.com/to/AZnTp8?typeform-source=mundolingo.org](https://form.typeform.com/to/AZnTp8?typeform-source=mundolingo.org)\\n\\nIf you‚Äôre invited to join your **[Local Embassy](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/GUZj246f3hBt927EWv_XtirgExr-3Xm97nI8nak8BY0),** you will be provided a link to **The Dark Room** by another Embassy resident.\\n\\n**Already in Residency? Continue below‚Ä¶**\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n## üëã Introduce yourself\\n\\nThis is a **must** if you want to socialise. Be noticed - Light up the sky üåü, don‚Äôt let anyone not-notice you arrived ‚ú® ‚Ä¶ or be a ‚Äú**lurker**‚Äù, it‚Äôs okay too.\\n\\n* Who are you?\\n* What are your passions, hobbies, interests?\\n* How did you get here?\\n* Why are you here?\\n* What kind of camera are you using?\\n* Do you have a website? Portfolio?\\n\\n### Pro-Tips\\n\\n* Use a nice photo and a real name to get a warmer reception.\\n\\n## üíæ Upload Photos\\n\\nPhotographers upload their photos to their **[Embassy](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/GUZj246f3hBt927EWv_XtirgExr-3Xm97nI8nak8BY0)** on Telegram.\\n\\n* 1 album of 30 to 40 photos as a ZIP file according to **[conditions](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/AVBqQwwn_yS7OH9EecXtPpcybdJ1xK_2H_pF4euL79c)**.\\n* 1 ‚Äútop pic‚Äù. Favourite photo from your album (not in the ZIP)\\n\\n## The Photographers Guide\\n\\nWhichever your level, from amateur to Pro, this guide holds vital resources for your work in Event Photography.\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/1whrv0SVEOekZOP0AVoSK5nfjgrOqgS-aPecUOaTHn8](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/1whrv0SVEOekZOP0AVoSK5nfjgrOqgS-aPecUOaTHn8)\\n\\n## üíé Share Resources\\n\\nThere‚Äôs a wealth of tips and tricks that Mundo Lingo Photographers have picked up over the years. Be open about what you learn, tricks for working with light, or getting that incredible angle, in the Dark Room. You will be appreciated for it\",\"timestamp\":1641722555,\"title\":\"The Dark Room\"},\"digest\":\"bL-FwW919Gr1HrhqBdn2JaBuEHKxUU44tzk_dyXIhPU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"nPK1tq8x6mIWNT4QtWbn2vxZ5OJnpLlNHcy4yJBPQ8o2gbJ8NCUw-BgBCOSbZRv7sW_0TJfBNQTPFQrvWnNF1A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x57d0f7cbea22222afabed23e09ac819f759269ea4cca2a83cdd992ddf3ffe88d22a7afd325b70c3c1ae7dee6f5fc8e22188ba69c589cf1f0528e258261121ae51b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"mMsMcopOXI0bNouEsFfzIW335FmcSaBZGPtNoeFuTJg\"}"